snippet.title: Man of Medan - Don't Play Alone - PS4/Xbox1/PC
snippet.description:
We said… Don’t Play Alone… and now you don’t have to. Introducing Man of Medan multiplayer modes! 2 player online co-op and 2-5 player couch co-op. Pre-order now: http://bnent.eu/TDPMoMCampaign
